race.description: Engineering By Stp Consultants 5Th Grade H
race.comment: NOAKI RADAR (3) is better than last start when fifth (22.11) in a Grade 5 at this track over 390m. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Can atone. SPRING MISTY (2) has been in sparkling form scoring back to back wins, the latest by 3.5 lengths (19.58) over 352m at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Hard to fault her recent form and can win again. OPTIMALITY (6) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her head turning win the start prior, getting around this track over 352m in 19.56. Has the ability and can find winning form again. GOLDSTAR KLEIN (5) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.
